#~ msgid "**connectivity**:"
#~ msgstr "**connectivity**:"

#~ msgid "``circular``: Qubits form a ring."
#~ msgstr "``circular``: Los cúbits forman un anillo."

#~ msgid "``linear``: Qubits are connected linearly."
#~ msgstr "``linear``: Los cúbits están conectados linealmente."

#~ msgid "``full``: All-to-all connectivity."
#~ msgstr "``full``: Conectividad todos a todos."

#~ msgid "Or a list of tuples explicitly specifying the connectivity."
#~ msgstr "O una lista de tuplas que especifiquen explícitamente la conectividad."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**one_qubit_gate**: Choose the parameterized "
#~ "single-qubit gate (e.g., "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.U1`, "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.U2`, "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.U3`)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**one_qubit_gate**: Elija la puerta "
#~ "parametrizada de un cúbit (p. ej., "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.U1`, "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.U2`, "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.U3`)."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**two_qubit_gate**: Choose the two-qubit "
#~ "interaction type (e.g., "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.CNOT`, "
#~ ":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.CZ`)."
